# Serene AI Dashboard · .env example
# Copy to .env and fill in values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   chmod 600 .env

# ──── Required ────
META_ACCESS_TOKEN=EAA...

# ──── Optional notification backends ────
# Configure ANY of these (the first one that works wins):

# Option 1: Telegram bot (recommended — fast & free)
#   1. Telegram → message @BotFather → /newbot → save token
#   2. Add bot to a channel/group, message it
#   3. Get chat_id: curl https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC...
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=-100123456789

# Option 2: CallMeBot (free WhatsApp, requires opt-in)
#   1. Send "I allow callmebot to send me messages" to +34 644 38 87 54
#   2. They reply with apikey
# CALLMEBOT_PHONE=+13053604406
# CALLMEBOT_APIKEY=1234567

# Option 3: Email via SMTP (Gmail App Password recommended)
#   1. Gmail → Account → Security → App Passwords → generate
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# SMTP_PORT=465
# SMTP_USER=sereneleparfum.team@gmail.com
# SMTP_PASS=app-password-here
# NOTIFY_TO=luiscala@example.com

# Option 4: Generic webhook (Slack, Discord, custom server)
# NOTIFY_WEBHOOK_URL=https://hooks.slack.com/services/...

# Option 5: Manual fallback — prints wa.me link to logs/console
# WHATSAPP_NUMBER=+13053604406
